headline: A Fresh Look at FIS Valuation Following Upbeat Q3 Results and Raised Growth Outlook
summary: Fidelity National Information Services (FIS) announced higher third-quarter earnings and revenue, both up from the prior year. The company also raised its revenue growth guidance for 2025, which signals confidence in ongoing business strength. See our latest analysis for Fidelity National Information Services.
